TY  - JOUR
T1  - Jump Regressions
AU  - Li, Jia
AU  - Todorov, Viktor
AU  - Tauchen, George
Y1  - 2017/01/01
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2017/01/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA12962
T2  - Econometrica
